{"body": "I'm just a little concerned about potential clients that the original change breaks.\r\n\r\n(Edit: quote from the spec turned out to be irrelevant here)\r\n\r\nThere might be a legitimate need to fix this on the server side to avoid breaking older clients that can't be easily updated (e.g. iOS as pointed out above).\r\n\r\nThat said, if the browser switched to 3 DP, it seems like a safe-bet that going forward, 3 DP should be well supported. It's just that at the moment when some clients can't parse the decimal fraction, the situation seems less than ideal.\r\n\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/24432315", "created_at": "2013-09-14T00:02:28Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/12226#issuecomment-24432315", "updated_at": "2013-09-14T00:22:47Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 12226, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/chancancode", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/22bb3e56828870ee9a0dd93aeadbe04a?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F8b407b57d02a2e41c7ba54441391d9ce.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/received_events", "gravatar_id": "22bb3e56828870ee9a0dd93aeadbe04a", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "chancancode", "type": "User", "id": 55829, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/chancancode/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237cdbabd3543c1510079c7"}, "id": 24432315, "issue_url": "https